content: we've teamed up with @foodforeveryone.aus artist @gemleslie to make two epic messina prints based on our dr. evil's magic mushroom & our pistachio praline!prints go on sale this monday via our website and will be super limited stock so if you've ever wanted to rep messina on your walls at home be sure to snap one up quick smart!a nice little bonus is that each print purchased provides 10 meals to @secondbiteorg - a charity which aims to feed those most in need  you can head to http://gelatomessina.com/.../food-for-everyone-x-messina... for more info @brettwalkerphotography
